nodes.text: This clone trooper captain served in the Grand Army of the Republic during the Clone Wars. In around 20 BBY, he was part of a mission to a moon besieged by the Confederacy of Independent Systems. Led by Grand Master Yoda, he helped evacuating the last of the moon's population. The clone trooper captain wore a Phase II clone trooper armor and was armed with a Z-6 rotary blaster cannon.
